  {
    "name": "section-hero",
    "content": "<!-- AI-IMAGE: emergency-hero-bg | Emergency page hero. Calm, professional clinical imagery that reassures.\n       SEARCH KEYWORDS: dental emergency care, reassuring clinical setting, urgent dental treatment room, on-call dentist.\n       REQUIREMENTS: Landscape, minimum 1920x800, professional quality.\n       FALLBACK: Any clean clinical operatory photo.\n       INSTRUCTION: Replace ONLY the url() value inside the section's background-image style; keep the linear-gradient overlay intact. Do not render this as an <img> element. -->\n<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero relative w-full min-h-[560px] md:min-h-[680px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden py-20 md:py-24 bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat text-ivory\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(15,23,42,0.75), rgba(15,23,42,0.55), rgba(15,23,42,0.85)), url('https://picsum.photos/1920/1080?random=160');\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\">\n\n    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-6\">\n      <span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero-component-eyebrow text-white text-xs font-medium tracking-widest uppercase font-sans\">Patient Information</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <h1 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero-component-title font-semibold leading-tight mb-6 text-white text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-serif\">\n      Dental Emergencies\n    </h1>\n\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero-component-subtitle text-white text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-sans\">\n      A sudden toothache, broken tooth, or dental injury requires immediate, professional attention. Our team is ready to relieve your pain and protect your smile, often the same day you call.\n    </p>\n\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero-component-urgency-note text-white font-medium text-base md:text-lg mb-10 font-sans\">\n      Do not wait. Time is critical in a dental emergency.\n    </p>\n\n    <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4\">\n      <a href=\"tel:\" class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero-component-cta-call inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent text-white px-7 py-4 rounded-full font-medium text-base transition-opacity hover:opacity-90 font-sans\">\n        <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z\"/></svg>\n        Call Now\n      </a>\n\n      <!-- AI-CONTENT: cta-label | Choose label by business.category:\n       - Endodontist / Endodontics → \"Book Appointment\"\n       - Orthodontist / Orthodontics → \"Schedule a Consultation\"\n       - Default / other dental → \"Request a Consultation\"\n       Apply the same label consistently across header, body, and footer CTAs for this site. -->\n\n      <a href=\"/consultation\" class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero-component-cta-appointment inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-4 rounded-full font-medium text-base transition-opacity hover:opacity-90 font-sans text-white border border-white/50\">\n        <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z\"/></svg>\n        Request a Consultation\n      </a>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>"
  },
  {
    "name": "section-emergency-types",
    "content": "<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types bg-white py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\">\n\n    <div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12 md:mb-16\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-5\">\n        <span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-eyebrow text-primary text-xs font-medium tracking-widest uppercase font-sans\">Recognizing Dental Emergencies</span>\n      </div>\n      <h2 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-title text-gray-900 font-semibold leading-snug mb-5 font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl\">\n        Common Dental <span class=\"text-primary\">Emergencies</span>\n      </h2>\n      <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-subtitle text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed font-sans\">\n        Dental emergencies require immediate attention to relieve pain, prevent infection, or save a tooth. Knowing what to look for helps you act fast, and acting fast can make all the difference.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8\">\n\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-card-1 bg-gray-100 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl p-8 flex flex-col gap-5\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-white\">\n          <svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-accent\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v4m0 4h.01M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 001.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 001.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 00-3.42 0z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-card-1-title text-gray-900 font-semibold text-xl mb-3 font-serif\">Severe Toothache</h3>\n          <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-card-1-description text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans mb-3\">Intense, persistent tooth pain often signals infection, deep decay, or nerve damage. Do not ignore throbbing or pressure that worsens with temperature changes.</p>\n          <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">If the pain is severe, sudden, or accompanied by swelling, contact us immediately for an evaluation.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-card-2 bg-gray-100 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl p-8 flex flex-col gap-5\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-white\">\n          <svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-accent\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-card-2-title text-gray-900 font-semibold text-xl mb-3 font-serif\">Knocked-Out Tooth</h3>\n          <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-card-2-description text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans mb-3\">A completely knocked-out (avulsed) tooth requires immediate action. The best chance of saving the tooth is treatment within 30 minutes of the injury.</p>\n          <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Handle the tooth by the crown only, never the root. Rinse gently if dirty and try to reinsert it, or store it in milk until you reach our office.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-card-3 bg-gray-100 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl p-8 flex flex-col gap-5\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-white\">\n          <svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-accent\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728A9 9 0 015.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-card-3-title text-gray-900 font-semibold text-xl mb-3 font-serif\">Cracked or Broken Tooth</h3>\n          <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-card-3-description text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans mb-3\">A cracked or fractured tooth can cause sharp pain when biting, sensitivity to temperature, or visible damage. Even hairline cracks can worsen quickly without treatment.</p>\n          <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Rinse with warm water, apply a cold compress to reduce swelling, and contact us right away to prevent further damage.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-card-4 bg-gray-100 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl p-8 flex flex-col gap-5\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-white\">\n          <svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-accent\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M19 7l-.867 12.142A2 2 0 0116.138 21H7.862a2 2 0 01-1.995-1.858L5 7m5 4v6m4-6v6m1-10V4a1 1 0 00-1-1h-4a1 1 0 00-1 1v3M4 7h16\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-card-4-title text-gray-900 font-semibold text-xl mb-3 font-serif\">Lost Filling or Crown</h3>\n          <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-card-4-description text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans mb-3\">A lost filling or crown exposes the underlying tooth structure, causing sensitivity and increasing the risk of further decay or fracture.</p>\n          <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Save the crown if possible. You can use dental wax or sugar-free gum as a temporary cover. Schedule an appointment promptly to avoid complications.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-card-5 bg-gray-100 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl p-8 flex flex-col gap-5\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-white\">\n          <svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-accent\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-2.5L13.732 4.5c-.77-.833-2.694-.833-3.464 0L3.34 16.5c-.77.833.192 2.5 1.732 2.5z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-card-5-title text-gray-900 font-semibold text-xl mb-3 font-serif\">Abscess or Infection</h3>\n          <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-card-5-description text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans mb-3\">A dental abscess is a pocket of pus caused by bacterial infection. Symptoms include severe pain, swelling, fever, and a bad taste in the mouth. Left untreated, the infection can spread.</p>\n          <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">An abscess will not resolve on its own. Contact us immediately, as untreated infections can become a serious health risk.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-card-6 bg-gray-100 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl p-8 flex flex-col gap-5\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-white\">\n          <svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-accent\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-card-6-title text-gray-900 font-semibold text-xl mb-3 font-serif\">Soft Tissue Injury</h3>\n          <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-emergency-types-component-card-6-description text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans mb-3\">Cuts, tears, or puncture wounds to the gums, tongue, cheeks, or lips can cause significant bleeding and pain. These injuries often occur alongside other dental trauma.</p>\n          <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Apply gentle pressure with clean gauze to control bleeding. If bleeding does not stop within 15 to 20 minutes, contact us or visit the nearest emergency room.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>"
  },
  {
    "name": "section-first-aid-steps",
    "content": "<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-first-aid-steps py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 bg-[#f5f5f4]\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\">\n\n    <div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12 md:mb-16\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-5\">\n        <span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-first-aid-steps-component-eyebrow text-primary text-xs font-medium tracking-widest uppercase font-sans\">Immediate Steps</span>\n      </div>\n      <h2 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-first-aid-steps-component-title text-gray-900 font-semibold leading-snug mb-5 font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl\">\n        What to Do <span class=\"text-primary\">Before You Reach Us</span>\n      </h2>\n      <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-first-aid-steps-component-subtitle text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed font-sans\">\n        Taking the right action before reaching our office can make the difference between saving and losing a tooth. Follow these guidelines for your specific situation.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8\">\n\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-first-aid-steps-component-card-1 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden flex flex-col\">\n        <div class=\"bg-primary px-6 py-5 flex items-center gap-4\">\n          <div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 bg-white/20\">\n            <span class=\"text-white font-serif text-lg font-semibold\">1</span>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-first-aid-steps-component-card-1-title text-white font-semibold text-lg leading-snug font-serif\">For a Knocked-Out Tooth</h3>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"px-6 py-6 flex flex-col flex-1\">\n          <ul class=\"space-y-4 flex-1\">\n            <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n              <span class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-primary text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 font-sans bg-black/[0.06]\">1</span>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Pick up the tooth by the crown (the chewing surface). Never touch the root.</p>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n              <span class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-primary text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 font-sans bg-black/[0.06]\">2</span>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Rinse the tooth gently with water if it is dirty. Do not scrub or remove any attached tissue.</p>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n              <span class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-primary text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 font-sans bg-black/[0.06]\">3</span>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Try to reinsert the tooth into the socket. If that is not possible, store it in a cup of milk or saliva.</p>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n              <span class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-primary text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 font-sans bg-black/[0.06]\">4</span>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Get to our office within 30 minutes for the best chance of saving the tooth.</p>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-first-aid-steps-component-card-2 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden flex flex-col\">\n        <div class=\"bg-primary px-6 py-5 flex items-center gap-4\">\n          <div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 bg-white/20\">\n            <span class=\"text-white font-serif text-lg font-semibold\">2</span>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-first-aid-steps-component-card-2-title text-white font-semibold text-lg leading-snug font-serif\">For a Toothache or Abscess</h3>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"px-6 py-6 flex flex-col flex-1\">\n          <ul class=\"space-y-4 flex-1\">\n            <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n              <span class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-primary text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 font-sans bg-black/[0.06]\">1</span>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Rinse your mouth thoroughly with warm salt water to cleanse the area and reduce bacteria.</p>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n              <span class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-primary text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 font-sans bg-black/[0.06]\">2</span>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Apply a cold compress to the outside of your cheek to help reduce swelling and numb the area.</p>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n              <span class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-primary text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 font-sans bg-black/[0.06]\">3</span>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Take over-the-counter pain relief as directed. Avoid aspirin directly on the gums, as it can burn tissue.</p>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n              <span class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-primary text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 font-sans bg-black/[0.06]\">4</span>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Avoid very hot or cold foods and drinks. Call our office to schedule an emergency appointment.</p>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-first-aid-steps-component-card-3 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden flex flex-col\">\n        <div class=\"bg-primary px-6 py-5 flex items-center gap-4\">\n          <div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 bg-white/20\">\n            <span class=\"text-white font-serif text-lg font-semibold\">3</span>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-first-aid-steps-component-card-3-title text-white font-semibold text-lg leading-snug font-serif\">For a Broken or Chipped Tooth</h3>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"px-6 py-6 flex flex-col flex-1\">\n          <ul class=\"space-y-4 flex-1\">\n            <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n              <span class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-primary text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 font-sans bg-black/[0.06]\">1</span>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Rinse your mouth with warm water to clean the area. Save any broken pieces if possible.</p>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n              <span class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-primary text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 font-sans bg-black/[0.06]\">2</span>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">If there is bleeding, apply clean gauze with gentle pressure until it stops.</p>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n              <span class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-primary text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 font-sans bg-black/[0.06]\">3</span>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Apply a cold compress to the outside of your mouth or cheek near the affected area to reduce swelling.</p>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n              <span class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-primary text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 font-sans bg-black/[0.06]\">4</span>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Cover any sharp edges with dental wax or sugar-free gum to protect your tongue and cheeks. Call us promptly.</p>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>"
  },
  {
    "name": "section-professional-care",
    "content": "<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-professional-care bg-white py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\">\n\n    <div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12 md:mb-16\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-5\">\n        <span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-professional-care-component-eyebrow text-primary text-xs font-medium tracking-widest uppercase font-sans\">Expert Emergency Care</span>\n      </div>\n      <h2 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-professional-care-component-title text-gray-900 font-semibold leading-snug mb-5 font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl\">\n        How Your Dentist <span class=\"text-primary\">Handles Emergencies</span>\n      </h2>\n      <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-professional-care-component-subtitle text-gray-600 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed font-sans\">\n        Our dental professionals are trained and equipped to diagnose and treat urgent dental conditions quickly and effectively, helping you find relief and protecting your long-term oral health.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-start mb-12 md:mb-16\">\n\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-professional-care-component-assessment-block rounded-3xl bg-gray-100 p-8 md:p-10\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-5\">\n          <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-200\">\n            <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-primary\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z\"/></svg>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"text-gray-900 font-serif text-xl font-semibold\">Immediate Assessment and Diagnosis</h3>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed mb-4 font-sans\">\n          When you arrive for an emergency visit, our team will perform a thorough clinical examination to identify the source and extent of the problem. We use digital X-rays and advanced imaging to get a precise diagnosis, even for issues that are not visible to the naked eye.\n        </p>\n        <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6 font-sans\">\n          A fast, accurate diagnosis is the foundation of effective emergency care. We will explain our findings clearly and walk you through your treatment options before proceeding.\n        </p>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-3\">\n          <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n            <span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5 bg-gray-200\">\n              <svg class=\"w-3 h-3 text-accent\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/></svg>\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Same-day pain relief</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n            <span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5 bg-gray-200\">\n              <svg class=\"w-3 h-3 text-accent\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/></svg>\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Digital imaging for precise diagnosis</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n            <span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5 bg-gray-200\">\n              <svg class=\"w-3 h-3 text-accent\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/></svg>\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Emergency extractions when necessary</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n            <span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5 bg-gray-200\">\n              <svg class=\"w-3 h-3 text-accent\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/></svg>\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Temporary and permanent restorations</span>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-professional-care-component-treatment-block rounded-3xl bg-gray-100 p-8 md:p-10\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-5\">\n          <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-200\">\n            <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-primary\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"/></svg>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"text-gray-900 font-serif text-xl font-semibold\">Treatment and Follow-Up</h3>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed mb-4 font-sans\">\n          Once we have identified the issue, your dentist will explain all available treatment options in plain language. We will discuss the benefits, risks, and expected outcomes of each approach so you can make an informed decision about your care.\n        </p>\n        <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6 font-sans\">\n          After treatment, we provide detailed recovery instructions and schedule a follow-up visit to monitor your healing. Our team is always available by phone if you have questions or concerns during your recovery.\n        </p>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-3\">\n          <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n            <span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5 bg-gray-200\">\n              <svg class=\"w-3 h-3 text-accent\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/></svg>\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Clear explanation of all treatment options</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n            <span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5 bg-gray-200\">\n              <svg class=\"w-3 h-3 text-accent\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/></svg>\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Written recovery and aftercare instructions</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n            <span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5 bg-gray-200\">\n              <svg class=\"w-3 h-3 text-accent\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/></svg>\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Scheduled follow-up to monitor healing</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n            <span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5 bg-gray-200\">\n              <svg class=\"w-3 h-3 text-accent\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/></svg>\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Phone support during your recovery period</span>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-professional-care-component-er-callout rounded-3xl bg-gray-100 p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\n        <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center bg-accent\">\n          <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-white\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-2.5L13.732 4.5c-.77-.833-2.694-.833-3.464 0L3.34 16.5c-.77.833.192 2.5 1.732 2.5z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h4 class=\"text-gray-900 font-semibold text-base font-sans mb-2\">When to Go to the Emergency Room</h4>\n          <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">While most dental emergencies are best treated in a dental office, some situations require immediate hospital attention. Go to the emergency room if you experience uncontrolled bleeding that does not stop with pressure, a suspected jaw fracture, difficulty breathing or swallowing, or severe facial swelling that is spreading rapidly. For all other dental emergencies, contact our office first for the fastest, most appropriate care.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>"
  },
