    "name": "section-why-choose-us",
    "content": "<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-why-choose-us py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 bg-gray-100\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\">\n\n    <div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12 md:mb-16\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-5\">\n        <span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-why-choose-us-component-eyebrow text-primary text-xs font-medium tracking-widest uppercase font-sans\">Why Patients Trust Us</span>\n      </div>\n      <h2 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-why-choose-us-component-title text-gray-900 font-semibold leading-snug mb-5 font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl\">\n        Emergency Care You Can <span class=\"text-primary\">Count On</span>\n      </h2>\n      <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-why-choose-us-component-subtitle text-gray-600 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed font-sans\">\n        When a dental emergency strikes, you need a team that responds quickly, treats with precision, and puts your comfort first.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8\">\n\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-why-choose-us-component-card-1 bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col gap-5\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-gray-100\">\n          <svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-accent\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 6v6l4 2m6-2a10 10 0 11-20 0 10 10 0 0120 0z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-why-choose-us-component-card-1-title text-gray-900 font-semibold text-xl mb-3 font-serif\">Same-Day Appointments</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans\">Dental emergencies do not follow a schedule, and neither do we. We do everything possible to accommodate same-day appointments so you get relief fast.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-why-choose-us-component-card-2 bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col gap-5\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-gray-100\">\n          <svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-accent\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-why-choose-us-component-card-2-title text-gray-900 font-semibold text-xl mb-3 font-serif\">Experienced Team</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans\">Our dentists and clinical staff bring years of training and hands-on experience to every emergency case. You are in skilled, steady hands when it matters most.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-why-choose-us-component-card-3 bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col gap-5\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-gray-100\">\n          <svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-accent\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-why-choose-us-component-card-3-title text-gray-900 font-semibold text-xl mb-3 font-serif\">Advanced Technology</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans\">We invest in modern diagnostic and treatment equipment, including digital X-rays and advanced imaging, to deliver faster, more accurate emergency care.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-why-choose-us-component-card-4 bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col gap-5\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-gray-100\">\n          <svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-accent\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-why-choose-us-component-card-4-title text-gray-900 font-semibold text-xl mb-3 font-serif\">Compassionate Care</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans\">We understand that dental emergencies are stressful and often painful. Our team approaches every patient with empathy, patience, and a genuine commitment to your well-being.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-why-choose-us-component-card-5 bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col gap-5\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-gray-100\">\n          <svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-accent\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-why-choose-us-component-card-5-title text-gray-900 font-semibold text-xl mb-3 font-serif\">Clear Communication</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans\">We never proceed without explaining what we have found and what we recommend. You will always know your options, the expected outcomes, and the costs involved before any treatment begins.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-why-choose-us-component-card-6 bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col gap-5\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-gray-100\">\n          <svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-accent\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-4.243-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z\"/><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-why-choose-us-component-card-6-title text-gray-900 font-semibold text-xl mb-3 font-serif\">Convenient Locations</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans\">With multiple office locations, you are never far from professional emergency dental care. We make it easy to get the help you need, when you need it.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>"
  },
  {
    "name": "section-cta",
    "content": "<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-cta py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 bg-gradient-brand text-ivory\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center\">\n\n    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-6\">\n      <span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-cta-component-eyebrow text-xs font-medium tracking-widest uppercase font-sans text-white/80\">Do Not Wait</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-cta-component-title text-white font-serif font-semibold leading-tight text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl mb-5\">\n      Get <span class=\"text-primary\">Relief</span> Now\n    </h2>\n\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-cta-component-description text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 font-sans text-white/80\">\n      Dental emergencies cannot wait, and neither should you. Our team is ready to see you as quickly as possible, including same-day appointments. Call us or request an emergency appointment online.\n    </p>\n\n    <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6\">\n      <a href=\"tel:\" class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-cta-component-cta-call inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-medium text-base transition-colors hover:opacity-90 font-sans\">\n        <svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z\"/></svg>\n        Call Now\n      </a>\n\n      <!-- AI-CONTENT: cta-label | Choose label by business.category:\n       - Endodontist / Endodontics → \"Book Appointment\"\n       - Orthodontist / Orthodontics → \"Schedule a Consultation\"\n       - Default / other dental → \"Request a Consultation\"\n       Apply the same label consistently across header, body, and footer CTAs for this site. -->\n\n      <a href=\"/consultation\" class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-cta-component-cta-appointment inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-medium text-base transition-colors hover:opacity-90 font-sans text-white/95 border border-black/20\">\n        <svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z\"/></svg>\n        Request a Consultation\n      </a>\n    </div>\n\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-cta-component-availability-note text-white/70 text-sm font-sans\">Available for same-day emergencies</p>\n\n  </div>\n</section>"
  }
]